Introduction

The Wind is a six-member boy group under With US Entertainment. As seven, they officially debuted on May 15, 2023, with their first mini album, "Beginning: The Wind Page".

The meaning behind the group name "The Wind" signifies the ambition to provide healing that is essential to many people, much like a gentle breeze. Just as the wind changes shape depending on the season, The Wind aims to stand "together" next to "us" by offering comfort, emotion, and pleasure in various ways at every moment.

The fandom name "WHIZ" represents the sound of the wind passing, signifying that the fans will cheer wherever The Wind goes.

On December 6, 2023, With US Entertainment announced that Member Shin Jaewon had departed from the group due to personal reasons.
